Marry me, Athena.

38:03.682 --> 38:05.951
-Bobby.
-I know it might feel
sudden and fast,

38:05.984 --> 38:07.853
but we both know how life works.

38:07.886 --> 38:09.688
-Yeah.
-Life is fleeting

38:09.721 --> 38:11.957
and it's precious, and when
you find happiness and you find

38:11.990 --> 38:13.659
