-I mean,

39:45.216 --> 39:47.185
I mean, I know
they call diamonds rocks,

39:47.218 --> 39:48.720
but this is a rock star.

39:48.754 --> 39:50.288
I mean, is your hand tired?

39:50.321 --> 39:51.757
'Cause I could help you
carry that,

39:51.790 --> 39:53.525
for a while,
if you need a little help.

39:53.559 --> 39:55.393
