41:06.131 --> 41:07.999
Well, who needs perfect?

41:08.033 --> 41:09.300
It's, uh...

41:09.334 --> 41:11.102
it's beautiful.

41:11.136 --> 41:13.505
So what made you change
your mind?

41:13.539 --> 41:16.041
MADDIE: The holidays with Doug,
they weren't a celebration.

41:16.074 --> 41:18.544
It was a performance.

41:18.577 --> 41:22.848
You know, pretending to be a...
happy couple that had it all.

41:22.881 --> 41:24.983
I just didn't want
to pretend this year.

41:25.016 --> 41:28.053
But then I realized
that he's taken enough from me.

41:28.086 --> 41:30.556
I'm not gonna let him take
one more thing,

41:30.589 --> 41:33.992
and I sure as hell am not
gonna let him take Christmas.

41:34.025 --> 41:36.461
Last year was
my worst Christmas ever.

41:36.494 --> 41:38.797
But maybe also my best,

41:38.830 --> 41:41.399
because that's the day
I decided to leave.

41:45.103 --> 41:48.406
Now, that is a good reason
to deck the halls.

